window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Battle across time! </p> <p>Belasarius apotheosis! </p> <p>Steamboats that launch Greek fire; telegraph lines connecting the battlefront on the Indus to ancient Constantinople, Byzantine palace plots aided by wireless devices: General Belasarius and his battle-hardened troops must advance quickly through the history of technology to stave off a coming age of ultimate darkness. And now - the epic final battle that will either give birth to or destroy Aide, Belasarius' doughty crystalline advisor and humanity's loyal friend! </p> <p>The latest entry in <i>New York Times</i> best seller Eric Flint and military SF master David Drake's groundbreaking Belasarius series.</p>"; 
